WEBVTT

00:01:41.079 --> 00:01:42.079
If you wish to flee

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.799
I can help you.

00:01:49.560 --> 00:01:52.000
Is a life of luxury not good?

00:01:53.319 --> 00:01:54.519
Why do you want to flee?

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.159
If you do not flee,

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.919
then let those who have hurt you

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.960
all pay the price.

00:02:18.199 --> 00:02:19.199
Miss Xiao Bai,

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.360
why do you say such things?

00:02:29.319 --> 00:02:30.280
Every day, Concubine Si,

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:32.599
in the Golden Pigeon Wine you serve the Manor Lord,

00:02:32.840 --> 00:02:34.000
you add a little something.

00:02:34.759 --> 00:02:37.199
It happens to clash with the elixirs the Manor Lord takes.

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:42.879
Doing this, Concubine Si,

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:45.080
how long until you get your wish?

00:02:46.919 --> 00:02:47.639
Five years?

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:49.879
Ten years?

00:02:57.479 --> 00:02:58.960
Why not join forces with us?

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:04.800
And let Heaven claim these villains sooner.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:30.159
That night, the Manor Lord came to my room as usual.

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:32.599
He drank a lot of wine

00:03:33.159 --> 00:03:34.680
and was in high spirits.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.199
But he didn't know...

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:38.919
that day

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:41.560
was his date with death.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.680
Playing tricks.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:29.920
Two months ago,

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.680
Lord Meng had traced the Yu'er case

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:33.920
to Baixiao Villa.

00:04:34.959 --> 00:04:36.680
He summoned the Manor Lord for questioning.

00:04:38.079 --> 00:04:38.680
However,

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:40.240
the Manor Lord

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.240
was killed by you.

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:49.120
Do you think he would really go to court?

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:52.480
Even if he went,

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:55.879
were you sure you could convict him?

00:04:57.079 --> 00:04:58.839
If you really had a way,

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:02.040
how could he still be at large until today?

00:05:04.959 --> 00:05:06.879
This was supposed to be a seamless plan.

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:10.879
I never thought Heaven would let us

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.600
meet again here and now.

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:15.759
Truly, man's plans are no match for Heaven's.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:22.759
Officer, tie us up and take us to the yamen quickly.

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:29.759
I will plead with the Three Judicial Offices.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.279
I will surely save your lives.

00:05:36.279 --> 00:05:37.199
Don't be silly.

00:05:38.399 --> 00:05:39.680
We killed someone.

00:05:41.319 --> 00:05:42.360
You did kill someone,

00:05:44.519 --> 00:05:46.399
but the person you killed also harmed you.

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:51.600
The Court of Judicial Review judges by law,

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:52.759
but also by reason and compassion.

00:05:54.279 --> 00:05:54.920
Don't worry.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.720
I will beg the Lord for leniency.

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:01.560
If he refuses,

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:04.600
I will go beg the Crown Prince.

00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:06.759
I will beg His Majesty.

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:23.279
I want to take Zhao Yun away.

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:28.079
I don't want to see

00:06:28.319 --> 00:06:29.720
your portraits on the wanted posters.

00:06:30.399 --> 00:06:32.199
Then I will take all the blame

00:06:32.399 --> 00:06:33.240
to protect her.

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:36.639
Do you take the Three Judicial Offices for fools?

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:39.800
Then what should we do?

00:06:40.519 --> 00:06:42.480
I can't just watch her go to her death.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.319
No matter what,

00:06:47.879 --> 00:06:49.480
good people shouldn't suffer endless grievances.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.920
And bad people must pay the price.

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:53.720
To break this deadlock,

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:55.839
the Eunuch Faction must die.

00:07:02.839 --> 00:07:04.839
By order of Nine Thousand Years, kill without mercy!

00:07:04.959 --> 00:07:05.639
Yes!

00:07:27.079 --> 00:07:28.639
Wait until tomorrow dawn

00:07:30.079 --> 00:07:32.079
You'll take me back to Dali Temple, right?

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:35.480
Rest assured

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:37.680
I will definitely take you away

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:40.879
I once hoped you were Zhao Yun

00:07:41.600 --> 00:07:42.920
Willing to bend the law for you

00:07:43.279 --> 00:07:44.480
And protect you at all costs

00:07:45.839 --> 00:07:46.720
But now

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:49.040
I hope you are Miss Xiao Bai

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.240
So I can handle the case impartially

00:07:51.519 --> 00:07:52.879
And stick to my principles

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.480
Zhao Yun moves my heart

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.800
Miss Xiao Bai gives me relief

00:08:04.399 --> 00:08:04.959
You

00:08:06.279 --> 00:08:06.920
I am not

00:08:08.199 --> 00:08:08.839
Zhao Yun

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.759
This contradictory hope

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:14.959
Makes me torn

00:08:19.079 --> 00:08:20.399
What should I do?

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:25.519
Worldly matters are heavy, but flowers are light

00:08:27.959 --> 00:08:28.720
Master Ye

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:30.680
Don't be trapped in the past

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.240
No matter how good the past was

00:08:34.519 --> 00:08:36.080
It is nothing but a fleeting illusion

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:41.879
I'm sorry

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:44.879
My Zhao Yun

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.240
Shouldn't have suffered so much

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.720
You are shielding a murderer

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.600
I've already lost you once

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:56.720
I can't lose you a second time

00:08:57.519 --> 00:08:58.080
Master Kun

00:08:58.480 --> 00:08:59.039
Master Kun

00:09:00.559 --> 00:09:01.120
What is it?

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:02.840
The Dark Investigation Division is attacking

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.279
I'll go request backup

00:09:04.519 --> 00:09:05.720
We're outnumbered, send them away first

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:06.960
Let's go to the secret cave

00:09:07.399 --> 00:09:07.759
Go

00:09:08.879 --> 00:09:09.120
Go

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:10.120
Go

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:16.679
Ye Li

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.080
Take Miss Xiao Bai and Concubine Si and go first

00:09:20.639 --> 00:09:21.200
How can I do that?

00:09:21.679 --> 00:09:22.200
There are so many people

00:09:22.639 --> 00:09:23.519
How can you handle them?

00:09:23.799 --> 00:09:24.559
There's no time

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:26.120
Take them and go, don't worry about me

00:09:26.840 --> 00:09:27.360
Master Kun

00:09:27.879 --> 00:09:28.879
You are still injured

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:29.840
Take them and go

00:09:30.039 --> 00:09:31.559
Don't worry, I'll be fine

00:09:33.399 --> 00:09:34.080
Master Kun

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:36.120
Go

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:42.759
Quick, come in

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:44.159
Find something to block the door

00:09:44.799 --> 00:09:45.200
Okay

00:09:52.519 --> 00:09:53.240
Ye Li, Miss Xiao Bai

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:54.000
I'm sorry

00:09:54.519 --> 00:09:55.679
I still have to go help him

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:56.600
Concubine Si

00:09:57.159 --> 00:09:57.960
Concubine Si

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:00.720
Concubine Si

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.519
Concubine Si

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:12.879
Didn't I tell you to leave?

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:13.720
Why did you come back?

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:35.000
Stop

00:10:38.759 --> 00:10:39.159
Quick, go

00:10:43.039 --> 00:10:43.600
Chase them

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:52.480
How are you?

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:55.559
I'm fine

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:57.879
Hold on

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.159
I will definitely get you out

00:11:00.639 --> 00:11:01.399
I'm not going

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:03.159
I'm not going

00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:06.600
I can't walk anymore

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:09.960
What are you saying?

00:11:11.159 --> 00:11:12.320
I will definitely get you out

00:11:12.559 --> 00:11:13.600
And find you the best doctor

00:11:14.159 --> 00:11:15.120
You will be fine

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:17.519
Your salary is next to nothing

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:19.720
Don't waste it

00:11:21.159 --> 00:11:22.279
I can afford it

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:25.679
I can't bear it

00:11:32.279 --> 00:11:33.080
This

00:11:35.919 --> 00:11:36.759
I leave to you

00:11:39.639 --> 00:11:40.799
You must remember

00:11:42.039 --> 00:11:43.360
In this manor

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.639
There was still a sister

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:56.240
I don't want it

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.159
I want you to go with me

00:12:05.279 --> 00:12:07.159
Such a fool

00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:10.320
Do you know?

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:13.000
That day you came to my room

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:17.120
Really

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:20.320
Really so silly

00:12:25.919 --> 00:12:27.159
Cherish what?

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:31.679
Cherish the person before you?

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:34.399
Wait until you're dressed

00:12:34.639 --> 00:12:35.639
I'll come find you again

00:12:45.879 --> 00:12:46.679
If you don't believe me,

00:12:46.840 --> 00:12:47.879
just cut me down.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:49.080
Concubine Si,

00:12:50.399 --> 00:12:51.399
I offended you earlier.

00:12:54.159 --> 00:12:55.080
Please accept my apology.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:58.720
I have plenty more tricks.

00:12:59.519 --> 00:13:00.480
Do you want to try me?

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:05.360
Don't you dare.

00:13:05.679 --> 00:13:06.720
She is my woman.

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:09.039
If she loses a single hair,

00:13:09.879 --> 00:13:11.159
you won't leave here alive.

00:13:16.519 --> 00:13:17.679
Come at me instead.

00:13:20.960 --> 00:13:21.759
I'm going with you.

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:23.840
No, don't drag me down.

00:13:24.519 --> 00:13:25.519
Then I'll kill myself.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:26.639
So I won't drag you down.

00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:28.559
Fine.

00:13:29.840 --> 00:13:30.799
Then stay close to me.

00:13:32.759 --> 00:13:33.240
Let's go.